WEBVTT

00:00:00.872 --> 00:00:04.584
Everyone says you have to get ready
to retire financially.

00:00:05.251 --> 00:00:06.961
And of course you do.

00:00:07.003 --> 00:00:08.379
But what they don't tell you

00:00:08.379 --> 00:00:12.300
is that you also have to get
ready psychologically.

00:00:13.217 --> 00:00:14.469
Who knew?

00:00:15.261 --> 00:00:18.222
But it's important
for a couple of reasons.

00:00:18.264 --> 00:00:24.020
First, 10,000 North Americans
will retire today

00:00:24.020 --> 00:00:27.982
and every day for the next 10 to 15 years.

00:00:28.441 --> 00:00:31.861
This is a retirement tsunami.